description.en:
Moses foldable shopping bag

Super cute shopping bag with a picture of the world map on it. The bag is extra sturdy and offers enough space for all your groceries and other stuff. It folds into a small world globe, so that you always take it with you easily.

Specifications:
Gender: junior
Age: 3+ years
Material: polyester
Dimensions: 38 x 56 cm (L x H)
Content: 9 liters
Color: multicolor
